nt origin, yet still allows the child window to access window.opener.location.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe solution, proposed by the reporter, was to add rel=\u0026quot;noreferrer noopener\u0026quot; to these external links.\u003c/p\u003e\n"},{"category":"researcher","can_view?":true,"can_create?":false}]}